106
00:05:24,900 --> 00:05:26,100
Mrs. Yan passed out?

107
00:05:26,660 --> 00:05:27,780
What to do now?

108
00:05:28,370 --> 00:05:30,220
After all, she is
Prime Minister’s wife.

109
00:05:30,250 --> 00:05:31,420
