140
00:06:48,300 --> 00:06:49,930
Your Highness!

141
00:06:50,980 --> 00:06:52,810
So elegant and gorgeous!

142
00:06:52,810 --> 00:06:55,020
-She is still in good health.
-Yeah.

143
00:06:55,020 --> 00:06:57,460
Still in fine fettle!

144
00:06:59,750 --> 00:07:00,190
Mom.

145
