156
00:07:30,050 --> 00:07:32,020
But my son is lovesick now.

157
00:07:32,020 --> 00:07:33,540
As his mother, I really feel sorry.

158
00:07:33,660 --> 00:07:36,130
So I acted rashly. Please forgive me.

159
00:07:36,730 --> 00:07:38,610
But if Princess Ban can marry
into our family,

160
00:07:38,980 --> 00:07:40,900
