171
00:08:01,170 --> 00:08:02,220
I don’t dare.

172
00:08:03,460 --> 00:08:06,730
But I think you will do His Majesty
this favor.

173
00:08:07,050 --> 00:08:09,900
Except my father and His Majesty,

174
00:08:10,050 --> 00:08:13,420
