183
00:08:33,370 --> 00:08:35,690
Now let me be clear here.

184
00:08:36,490 --> 00:08:38,690
Even if there is only Yan Zhen
in this world,

185
00:08:38,850 --> 00:08:40,330
I’d rather become a nun

186
00:08:40,380 --> 00:08:41,780
than marry your son!

187
00:08:41,810 --> 00:08:43,660
Princess, you’re still young.

188
00:08:44,140 --> 00:08:46,620
I won’t blame you for being rude.

189
00:08:47,210 --> 00:08:50,090
But the marriage is not up to you.

190
00:08:50,620 --> 00:08:53,090
The Yans and the Bans are both
favored by His Majesty.

191
00:08:53,260 --> 00:08:54,420
I think His Majesty will

192
00:08:54,570 --> 00:08:56,300
definitely agree to the marriage
between us.

193
00:08:56,420 --> 00:08:57,900
As long as he allows,

194
00:08:58,050 --> 00:09:00,260
there’ll be no place for you to escape.

195
00:09:00,450 --> 00:09:02,020
Don’t scare me with His Majesty.

196
00:09:02,500 --> 00:09:03,810
We’re both not sure whom

197
00:09:03,850 --> 00:09:04,690
His Majesty will listen to.

198
00:09:04,970 --> 00:09:06,140
Your family

199
00:09:06,140 --> 00:09:07,930
is just good at acting shamelessly.

200
00:09:08,210 --> 00:09:09,740
These stupid ways can’t

201
00:09:09,970 --> 00:09:11,330
influence His Majesty’s decision.

202
00:09:11,850 --> 00:09:13,210
Mrs. Yan, that’s totally right.

203
00:09:14,020 --> 00:09:15,300
To deal with your family,

204
00:09:15,300 --> 00:09:16,900
these stupid ways are enough.

205
00:09:17,780 --> 00:09:20,050
But if you like,

206
00:09:20,620 --> 00:09:22,850
I’m willing to play it with you.

207
00:09:23,260 --> 00:09:25,300
So, take care.

208
00:09:32,140 --> 00:09:34,570
Your grandma is Her Highness, so what?

209
00:09:35,050 --> 00:09:36,300
After you marry my son,

210
00:09:36,570 --> 00:09:38,420
I have plenty of ways to deal with you.

211
00:09:39,850 --> 00:09:40,690
Your Majesty.

212
00:09:43,090 --> 00:09:44,170
Your Majesty,

213
00:09:44,740 --> 00:09:46,740
my wife strived for the marriage,

214
00:09:46,850 --> 00:09:48,850
so she offended Her Highness.

215
00:09:48,900 --> 00:09:50,810
Please forgive us.

216
00:09:53,740 --> 00:09:56,300
Since she offended Princess Royal,

217
00:09:56,780 --> 00:09:59,330
