for forgiveness.

218
00:10:02,930 --> 00:10:06,260
I’m afraid Her Highness is still mad

219
00:10:06,260 --> 00:10:07,570
and doesn’t want to see me.

220
00:10:08,020 --> 00:10:10,620
Her Highness is Your Majesty’s aunt,

221
00:10:10,900 --> 00:10:12,540
as long as you talk to her,

222
00:10:12,850 --> 00:10:16,170
I think she will cool down.

223
00:10:18,780 --> 00:10:21,050
Of course she is my aunt.

224
00:10:21,330 --> 00:10:23,450
But this is all about your son.

225
00:10:24,210 --> 00:10:25,810
If you want my aunt to forgive you,

226
00:10:26,660 --> 00:10:28,810
you’d better go to her yourself.

227
00:10:30,930 --> 00:10:33,500
Your Majesty, I asked

228
00:10:33,690 --> 00:10:35,780
my wife to go for the proposal

229
00:10:36,140 --> 00:10:38,020
just for the situation of the court.

230
00:10:38,050 --> 00:10:39,740
For situation of the court?

231
00:10:39,810 --> 00:10:40,780
That’s right.

232
00:10:41,210 --> 00:10:42,810
I wonder if Your Majesty have ever
thought about it.

233
00:10:42,970 --> 00:10:44,620
When the Prince succeeds to the throne,

234
00:10:44,900 --> 00:10:45,970
the Shis

235
00:10:45,970 --> 00:10:49,050
will take the lead in the court.

236
00:10:49,330 --> 00:10:51,020
I’m afraid I will be

237
00:10:51,020 --> 00:10:53,500
too weak to contain them alone.

238
00:10:53,500 --> 00:10:54,970
If they can keep their duty,

239
00:10:55,260 --> 00:10:57,420
that’ll be great for the country.

240
00:10:57,540 --> 00:10:59,850
But what if they have any bad idea?

241
00:10:59,930 --> 00:11:01,450
That’ll be a big problem.

242
00:11:01,620 --> 00:11:05,330
So, if we can unite with the Bans
by marriage,

243
00:11:05,570 --> 00:11:08,930
