Where is beautiful?

327
00:15:23,540 --> 00:15:25,210
I just like the scenery in this alley.

328
00:15:26,810 --> 00:15:28,660
Then, enjoy your time. See you.

329
00:15:28,740 --> 00:15:29,420
See you.

330
00:15:37,090 --> 00:15:37,850
Mr. Du,

331
00:15:38,850 --> 00:15:40,900
I have spread the gossip that

332
00:15:40,900 --> 00:15:42,050
the country can’t live without
the Yans.

333
00:15:42,210 --> 00:15:43,020
Please pay me now.

334
00:15:43,050 --> 00:15:43,930
Miss Softy,

335
00:15:43,970 --> 00:15:45,380
I have settled down the matter about
the “coquette”.

336
00:15:45,380 --> 00:15:46,570
Please pay me the rest of the money.

337
00:15:49,620 --> 00:15:51,780
-It’s you who are spreading the rumor!
